Hello you! Thank you for the visit. I am artist that creates things around my mood and interest of the moment.

summary: “A shadow emerged from the dark of the wood. It stood in front of Royce. Tall, it was, and gaunt and hard as old bones, with...
caption:
“A shadow emerged from the dark of the wood. It stood in front of Royce. Tall, it was, and gaunt and hard as old bones, with flesh pale as milk. Its armor seems to change color as it moved; here it was white as new-fallen snow, there it was black as shadow, everywhere dappled with the deep grey-green of the trees. The patterns ran like moonlight on water with every step it took.
Will heard the breath go out of Ser Waymar Royce in a long hiss. “Come no farther,” the lordling warned. His voice cracked like a boy’s. He threw the long sable cloak back over his shoulders, to free his arms for battle, and took his sword in both hands. The wind had stopped. It was very cold.
The other slid forward on silent feet. In its hand was a longsword like none that Will had ever seen. No human metal had gone into the forging of that blade. It was alive with moonlight, translucent, a shard of crystal so thin that it seemed almost vanish when seen edge-on. There was a faint blue shimmer to the thing, a ghost-light that played around its edges, and somehow Will knew it was sharper than any razor…”

Tome 1, page 14, A game of thrones.

I bought the books, and I’m feeling inspired by them. This long lines is what I wanted to paint on this illustration. The guy was not cocky as pictured in the Serie, he was courageous for an 18 young man. I mixed the details of the book, some of the Serie and added my spices. Every interpretation deserves to be alive.

title: Game of Thrones Rewatch 1.09
body:
1. The Stark theme gets me low key hype.

2. “Father rots in a dungeon. How long will it be before they take off his head?” This episode, actually, Robb.

3. It’s funny because I’m watching GoT on my computer and Harry Potter is on the TV so I’m seeing Walder Frey and Filch at the same time and now that meme is in my head

4. Aww Mormont giving Jon Longclaw and everyone wanting to look at it.

5.”Did you get a look at his daughter?” *Theon snickers* Man, they did that dynamic dirty.

6. Also I’ll say it for the hundredth time, legit, Robb, you could’ve married a Frey girl and kept Talisa as your mistress or second wife or whatever an just treat them both honourably, my god. Or you could’ve married Talisa when the war was done and been like SIKE.

7. “Surely there are ways to have me killed that would be less detrimental to the war effort!” Wonderful, wonderful lines.

8, SHAE. She and Tyrion were so cute.

9, More dead animals.

10. “Half man! Half man! Half man!” What a chant.

11. Ayyyye Robb capturing Jaime!

12. “If we do it your way, kingslayer, you’d win.” See how smart you were??

13. Arya, the baker man left, you could’ve legit just stolen those pastries.

14. Sansa pleading for Ned when he’s about to be decapitated is also underrated.

15. Yea, I remember thinking … this didn’t happen, it’s a dream or it’s a hallucination, it’s something but it’s not real!!
